    <label>Jeub</label>
    <description>''Dude, let me in! I'm a fairy! DON'T YOU BELIEVE IN FAIRIES?'' \n \n Jeubs (pronounced "Jeb") are small, eusocial, goblin-like fairies notable for their distinctly ears and aggressive behavior. Jeubs are violent, simple-minded predators that will gladly eat their own kind when available. Whereas most animals' outer ears are bendable and comprised of cartilage, the cartilage on a Jeub's ear only exists at the tips. This is because the base of the Jeub ear leading into the ear canal is actually solid bone. This makes a Jeub skeleton instantly recognizable. \n \n Normal Jeubs do not have sapience, but are capable of following advanced orders if a sapient being directs them. In fact, Jeubs are the grunts and expendable foot soldiers of any Jeub civilization: sapient Jeubs are called High Jeubs, are less insane, and actually control the society.</description>
